snippet.title: Brandish 2: The Planet Buster [English] for SNES/Super Famicom Gameplay Sample
snippet.description:
Brandish 2: The Planet Buster was only released in Japan by Falcom for the Super Famicom (SNES). This hack and slash game picks up where the original left off and is available in English thanks to a fan translation.
